INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (236, '''We''re going to play elephants and circuses,'' said a little boy at kindergarten, ''Do you want to join in?''''I''d love to,''replied the teacher. ''What do you want me to do?''''You can be the lady that feeds us peanuts !''');
