INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1400, 'A woman went to a sweet store to buy some sweets. The boy behind the counter said "Gosh, your ugly aren''t you?, I''ve never seen anyone so hideous as you before""Young man" she replied. " I didn''t come here to be insulted""Really", he said, "Where do you usually go ?"');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1401, 'Little Johnny and his mother were on a train. Johnny leant over and started to whisper in his mother''s ear.''Johnny, how many times have I told you,'' said his mother, '' it''s rude to whisper. If you have something to say, say it out loud.''''OK, said Johnny, ''why does the lady over there look like an ugly, haggard old witch ?''');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1402, 'Girlfriend: Will you love me when I''m old and fat and ugly?Boyfriend: Of course I do !');
