INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1406, 'Bill: My sister has lovely long red hair all down her back.Will: Pity it''s not on her head.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1407, 'Julie had broken off her engagement. Her friend asked her what had happened. ''I thought it was love at first sight,'' said Julie. ''It was, but it was the second and third sights that changed my mind.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1408, 'Beautician: Did that mud pack I gave you for your girlfriend improve her appearance ?Man: It did for a while - then it fell off.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1409, 'Two teenage boys were talking in the classroom. One said, ''I took my girlfriend to see ''The bride of Dracula'' last night.''''Oh yeah,'' said the other, '' what was she like ?''''Well she was about six foot six, white as a ghost and she had big red staring eyes and fangs.''The other said, ''Yes, but what was ''The Bride of Dracula'' like ?''');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (1410, 'I can''t understand why people say my girlfriend''s legs look like matchsticks. They do look like sticks - but they certainly don''t match.');
