INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2353, 'Why did the Scottish cannibal live on a sugar plantation?He said, "So that I can feed my lads with m''lasses."');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2354, 'Why do cannibals make suitcases out of people''s heads? Because they''re headcases.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2355, 'What happened when a cannibal went on a self-catering holiday? He ate himself.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2356, 'First cannibal: I can''t find anything to eat! Second cannibal: But the jungle''s full of people. First cannibal: Yes, but they''re all very unsavory.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2357, 'Did you hear about the cannibals who captured a scrawny old hunter? It sure gave them something to chew over.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2358, 'Did you hear about the cannibal family who were caught spying by the witch-doctor? They were given a right roasting.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2359, 'Two cannibals were having their dinner. One said to the other "I don''t like your friend." The other one said, "Well, put him to one side and just eat the vegetables."');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2360, 'The cannibal priest told his flock to close their eyes and say grace. "For whosoever we are about to eat, may the Lord make us truly thankful."');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2361, '"Well, children," said the cannibal cooking teacher. "What did you make of the new English teacher?" "Burgers, ma''am."');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2362, 'Two cannibals were having lunch. "Your wife makes a great soup," said one to the other. "Yes!" agreed the first. "But I''m going to miss her terribly."');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2363, 'First Cannibal: Who was that girl I saw you with last night? Second Cannibal: That was no girl, that was my supper.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2364, 'Did you hear about the cannibal who joined the police force?He said he wanted to grill his suspects.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2365, 'Did you hear about the cannibal who commited suicide? He got himself into a real stew.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2366, 'Cannibals capture three men. The men are told that they will be skinned and eaten and then their skin will be used to make canoes. Then they are each given a final request. The first man asks to be killed as quickly and painlessly as possible. His request is granted, and they poison him. The second man asks for paper and a pen so that he can write a farewell letter to his family. This request is granted, and after he writes his letter, they kill him saving his skin for their canoes. Now it is the third man''s turn. He asks for a fork. The cannibals are confused, but it is his final request, so they give him a fork. As soon as he has the fork he begins stabbing himself all over and shouts, "To hell with your canoes!"');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2367, 'A cannibal son and his father are out looking for food. They are watching people walk down the street. The son suggested a particularly plump woman and the father rejected saying that she''s too fatty. Later on the son asked about a very skinny woman. Again the father refused saying that she''s to skinny. After a while the son pointed out a very attractive woman." sure son" the father replied, drooling. "We''ll take her home and eat you mother!"');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2368, 'Q. What did the cannibal''s wife give her husband when he came home late for dinner? A. The cold shoulder.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2369, 'First cannibal: We had burglars last night. Second cannibal: Did they taste good?');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2370, 'First cannibal: I don''t know what to make of my husband these days. Second cannibal: How about a curry?');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2371, 'The cannibal king was having dinner when a servant came running in. "Your Majesty," he said, "the slaves are revolting!""You don''t have to tell me," said the king. "I''m trying to eat them. "Where did we get these slaves anyway?""From the country next door," replied the servant. "We must get a new butcher," said the king. "Bring me Delia Smith." "We can''t, Your Majesty, she''s still cooking for you." "Well, bring her to me once she''s crispy enough," said the king.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2372, 'What does a cannibal call a skateboarder? Meals on wheels.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2373, 'What is the cannibals'' favorite game? Swallow my Leader.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2374, 'What happened to the cannibal lion? He had to swallow his pride.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2375, 'Did you hear about the cannibal who went vegetarian?He couldn''t stop eating swedes.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2376, 'Cannibal Boy: I''ve brought a friend home for dinner. Cannibal Mom: Put him in the fridge and we''ll have him tomorrow.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2377, 'A cannibal chief was just about to stew his latest victim for dinner when the man protested, "You can''t eat me ? I''m the manager!" "Well," said the cannibal, "soon you''ll be a manager in chief."');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2378, 'First cannibal: My wife''s a tough old bird. Second cannibal: You should have left her in the oven for another half an hour.');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2379, 'A cannibal''s dillema: If God didn''t want us to eat people, why did he make them out of meat?');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2380, 'A man is captured by cannibals, every day they poke him with spears and use his blood to wash down their food.Finally the guy calls the chief over and says, "Hey, you can kill me or you can eat me, but I''m tired of getting stuck for drinks!"');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2381, 'Cannibal: Mom, mom, I''ve been eating a missionary and I feel sick !Mom: Well, you know what they say - you can''t keep a good man down !');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2382, 'Was the principal''s brother really a missionary?He certainly was. He gave the people of the Cannibal Islands their first taste of Christianity !');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2383, 'When a plane caught fire over the jungle the pilot ejected and landed in a cannibal''s pot. The cannibal turned to his friend and said, ''What''s this flier doing in my soup?''');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2384, '1st Cannibal: I don''t know what to make of my boyfriend these days.2nd Cannibal: How about a hotpot ?');
INSERT INTO jokes VALUES (2385, 'What did the cannibal''s parents say when she brought her boyfriend home ?''Lovely, dear, he looks good enough to eat!''');
